-with-sundays-bests-jessica-reedy/|author=TL|title=Real Talk with Sunday's Best's Jessica Reedy|publisher=Hear What I Hear|date=6 January 2011}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Dianne|Reeves}} || 1956\u2013 || American ||   || style=text-align:center|<ref>{{cite web|work=The Guardian|title=Prom 27: Ella and Dizzy: A Centenary Tribute review \u2013 virtuosic hat tip to jazz legends' greatest hits|author=Lewis, John|date=6 August 2017|accessdate=30 August 2017|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2017/aug/06/prom-27-ella-and-dizzy-a-centenary-tribute-review-virtuosic-hat-tip-to-jazz-legends-greatest-hits}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url = https://www.nytimes.com/1992/02/18/arts/review-pop-dianne-reeves-s-flavorings.html| title = Review/Pop; Dianne Reeves's Flavorings| work=[[The New York Times]]| date=18 February 1992| accessdate=10 April 2018| first=Stephen| last=Holden}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url = https://mg.co.za/article/2014-09-26-00-an-ode-to-trailblazing-jazz-singers| title = An ode to trailblazing jazz singers| work=[[Mail & Guardian]]| date=26 September 2014| accessdate=10 April 2018| first=Stefanie| last=Jason}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Martha|Reeves}} || 1941\u2013 || American || {{hlist| [[Martha and the Vandellas]] | [[The Fascinations]]}} || style=text-align:center|<ref name=\"Martha\"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.buzzmag.co.uk/martha-reeves-the-vandellas-live-review/|title=MARTHA REEVES & THE VANDELLAS LIVE REVIEW|first=Nick|last=Merriman|date=18 December 2013|accessdate=15 May 2019|work=Buzz Magazine}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://reviewfix.com/2012/08/goldenlane-records-release-two-rb-live-concert-dvds-martha-reeves-and-the-ojays/|author=Staff|title=GOLDENLANE RECORDS RELEASE TWO R&B LIVE CONCERT DVDS: MARTHA REEVES AND THE O'JAYS|date=31 August 2012|accessdate=15 May 2019|work=Review Fix}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.musicradar.com/news/guitars/the-30-greatest-lead-singers-of-all-time-315448|author=MusicRadar|title=The 30 greatest lead singers 