ardian]]| date=23 July 2011| accessdate=1 April 2018| first=Tracy| last=McVeigh}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/culture-obituaries/tv-radio-obituaries/8657695/Amy-Winehouse.html| title = Amy Winehouse: Obituary| work=[[The Daily Telegraph]]| date=24 July 2011| accessdate=1 April 2018| first=| last=}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Lizz|Wright}} || 1980\u2013 || American || || style=text-align:center|<ref>{{cite journal|work=Billboard|title=Hidden Beach Label Shoring Up More Talent|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8A0EAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA26&dq=oleta+adams+contralto&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwi41oH8_ovWAhVH42MKHYsiDqoQ6AEIKDAA#v=onepage&q=oleta%20adams%20contralto&f=false|date=21 June 2003|p=26|via=Google Books}} {{open access}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url = https://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=88666000| title =Lizz Wright in Concert| work=[[National Public Radio|NPR]]| date=21 March 2008| accessdate=7 April 2018| first=| last=}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url = https://www.theguardian.com/music/2005/nov/06/jazz| title =Voice of the people| work=[[The Guardian]]| date=6 November 2005| accessdate=7 April 2018| first=Stuart| last=Nicholson}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Rachael|Yamagata}} || 1977\u2013 || American ||   || style=text-align:center|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.readersdigest.co.uk/culture/music/10-best-records-of-2017|title=10 Best records of 2017|accessdate=25 March 2020|date=11 December 2017|work=[[Reader's Digest]]|last=Mackevic| first=Eva}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=https://americansongwriter.com/rachael-yamagata-threatening-cynicism/|first=Lynne|last=Margolis|title=RACHAEL YAMAGATA: Threatening Cynicism|accessdate=25 March 2020|date=27 October 2008|work=[[American Songwriter]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|work=[[The New York Times]]|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/27/arts/music/27yama.html|first=Jon|last=Pareles|title=Currents of Regret, with Sparks of Spite|accessdate=25 March 2020| date=26 September 2008}}</ref><