ne Anderson, original Airplane singer, dead at 74|work=USA Today|date=1 February 2016|author=Italie, Hillel|accessdate=4 September 2016|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/people/2016/02/01/signe-anderson-dead/79627978/}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url = https://www.nytimes.com/2016/02/02/arts/music/signe-anderson-jefferson-airplane-singer-dies-at-74.html| title = Signe Anderson, Jefferson Airplane Singer, Dies at 74| work=[[The New York Times]]| date=2 February 2016| accessdate=5 April 2018| first=| last=}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url = https://www.sfgate.com/music/article/Signe-Toly-Anderson-original-singer-for-6797458.php| title = Signe Toly Anderson, original Jefferson Airplane singer, dies| work=[[San Francisco Chronicle]]| date=1 February 2016| accessdate=5 April 2018| first=Aidin| last=Vaziri}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Inez|Andrews}} || 1929\u20132012 || American ||  || style=text-align:center|{{sfn|Bogdanov et al.|2002|pages=590, 594}}<ref>{{cite news| url = https://www.nytimes.com/2012/12/22/arts/music/inez-andrews-gospel-singer-dies-at-83.html| title = Inez Andrews, Gospel Singer, Dies at 83| work=[[The New York Times]]| date=21 December 2012| accessdate=5 April 2018| first=Dennis| last=Hevesi}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url = http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2012-12-19/entertainment/ct-ent-1220-inez-andrews-obit-20121219_1_albertina-walker-gospel-inez-andrews| title = Inez Andrews, towering gospel artist, dead at 83| work=[[Chicago Tribune]]| date=19 December 2012| accessdate=5 April 2018| first=Howard| last=Reich}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sortname|LaVerne|Andrews|The Andrews Sisters}} || 1911\u20131967 || American || [[The Andrews Sisters]] || style=text-align:center|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.avclub.com/r-i-p-patty-andrews-last-remaining-member-of-the-andr-1798236066|title=R.I.P. Patty Andrews, last remaining member of The Andrews Sisters|first=Marah|last=Eakin|date=30 January 2013|accessdate=10 June 2019|work=[[The A.V. Club]]}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Anggu