azzles-go-broke-portrayal-judy-garland| title = Ren\u00e9e Zellweger Dazzles In A Go-For-Broke Portrayal Of Judy Garland| work=[[High Plains Public Radio|HPPR]] |first=Justin| last=Chang| date=26 September 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n{{clear}}\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of mezzo-sopranos in non-classical music]]\n* [[List of sopranos in non-classical music]]\n* [[List of basses in non-classical music]]\n* [[List of baritones in non-classical music]]\n* [[List of tenors in non-classical music]]\n* [[List of operatic contraltos]]\n* [[Voice classification in non-classical music]]\n* [[Voice type]]\n\n==Notes==\n{{Noteslist}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==Works cited==\n* {{cite book|last=Abjorensen|first=Norman|year=2017|title=Historical Dictionary of Popular Music|publisher=Rowman & Littlefield|ref=harv|isbn= 978-1-538-10215-2}}\n* {{Cite book|title=Rock-N-Roll Gold Rush |last=Dean |first= Maury|authorlink= |coauthors= |year= 2003|publisher= Algora Publishing|location= |isbn= 0-87586-207-1| ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|ref={{SfnRef|Bogdanov et al.|2002}} |title=All Music Guide to Rock: The Definitive Guide to Rock, Pop, and Soul |publisher=Hal Leonard Corporation/Backbeat Books |year=2002 |last1=Bogdanov |first1=Vladimir |last3=Woodstra |first3=Chris |last2=Erlewine |first2=Stephen Thomas |isbn=978-0-87930-653-3 |oclc=47823606}}\n* {{cite book|last=Sullivan|first=Steve|title=Encyclopedia of Great Popular Song Recordings|volume=1|publisher=Scarecrow Press|isbn=978-0-810-88296-6|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Weller|first=Sheila|title=Girls Like Us: Carole King, Joni Mitchell, Carly Simon--And the Journey of a Generation|year=2008|publisher=Simon and Schuster|isbn= 978-0-743-49147-1|ref=harv}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Contraltos In Non-Classical Music}}\n[[Category:Contraltos| ]]\n[[Category:Lists of singers]]\n[[Category:Lists of women in music]]\n", "name_user": "Davemck", "label": "safe", "comment": "rename duplicate parm", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_contraltos_in_non-classical_music"}
{"title_page": "Karanpur", "text_new": "{{About|the city|the tehsil|Karanpur tehsil}}\n{{Cleanup|date=April 2011}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2018}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=May 2018}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name                    = Karanpur\n| native_name             = Sri Karanpur \n| artist_from_karanpur    = Onenesslover \n| settlement_type         = city\n| image_skyline           = \n| image_alt               = \n| image_caption           = \n| pushpin_map             = India Rajasthan#India\n| pushpin_label_position  = right\n| pushpin_map_alt         = \n| pushpin_map_caption     = Location in Rajasthan, India\n| coordinates             = {{coord|29.8414|N|73.4547|E|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type        = Country\n| subdivision_name        = {{flag|India}}\n| subdivision_type1       = [[States and territories of India|State]]\n| subdivision_name1       = [[Rajasthan]]\n| subdivision_type2       = [[List of districts of India|District]]\n| subdivision_name2       = [[Ganganagar district|Ganganagar]]\n| established_title       = <!-- Established -->\n| established_date        = \n| founder                 = \n| named_for               = \n| government_type         = \n| governing_body          = \n| unit_pref               = Metric\n| area_footnotes          = \n| area_rank               = \n| area_total_km2          = \n| elevation_footnotes     = \n| elevation_m             = 185\n| population_total        = 20694\n| population_as_of        = 2001\n| population_rank         = \n| population_density_km2  = auto\n| population_demonym      = \n| population_footnotes    = \n| demographics_type1      = Languages\n| demographics1_title1    = Official\n| demographics1_info1     = [[Hindi language|Hindi]]\n| timezone1               = [[Indian Standard Time|IST]]\n| utc_offset1             = +5:30\n| postal_code_type        = [[Postal Index Number|PIN]]\n| postal_code             = 335073\n| registration_plate      = \n| website                 = \n| footnotes               = \n}}\n'''Sri Karanpur''' is a town and a [[municipality]] (Tehsil) in [[Ganganagar district]] in the [[India]]n [[States and territories of India|state]] of [[Rajasthan]]. Karanpupr De Munde is famous rap song of Sri Karanpur by Onenesslover aka Arpit Makkar.\n\n==An artist that Sri Karanpur takes pride in==\nAn artist who is famous by a rap song \"Karanpur De Munde <ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sfk5XGeH4-E</ref>\" written and sung by Onenesslover aka Arpit Makkar.Onenesslover is rapper and hip hop artist.He believes that people remember them from their catchy hooks.\n\n==Geography==\nSri Karanpur is located at {{Coord|29.8414|N|73.4547|E|}}.<ref>[http://www.fallingrain.com/world/IN/24/Karanpur.html Falling Rain Genomics, Inc - Karanpur]</ref> It has an average elevation of 185&nbsp;metres (606&nbsp;feet).\n\n==Demographics==\n{{As of|2001|alt=As of the [[2001 Census of India]]}},<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.censusindia.net/results/town.php?stad=A&state5=999|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20040616075334/http://www.censusindia.net/results/town.php?stad=A&state5=999|archivedate=2004-06-16|title= Census of India 2001: Data from the 2001 Census, including cities, villages and towns  (Provisional)|accessdate=2008-11-01|publisher= Census Commission of India}}</ref> Sri Karanpur had a population of 20,694. Males constitute 53% of the population and females 47%. Karanpur has an average literacy rate of 64%, higher than the national average of 59.5%: male literacy is 71%, and female literacy is 56%. In Karanpur, 14% of the population is under 6 years of age. Major languages spoken here are [[Punjabi language|Punjabi]] and [[Bagri language|Bagri]].\n\n== Economy And popularity ==\nSri Karanpur once produced the best quality cotton in India and even attracted Birlas to set up a mill which still exists today in the town, but after 1995 the produce took a deep dip and people shifted to other cash crops. Today it is known in the area to have most fertile land supporting thousands of acre under horticulture especially the kinnow which is exported to west Asia.{{cn|date= August 2017}}\n\n==Sri Karanpur Market==\nSri Karanpur, also known as Mandi Karanpur is famous for dealing of various crops namely cotton, barley and wheat.\nThe old mandi now a Bazaar famous among many nearby villages consists of many cloths, jewelers, restaurants and Sweets shops. Nagpal Sweet House is one of the oldest and most famous Sweet shop famous among many people from districts of Rajasthan, Punjab and Delhi.and a bazaar of vegetables. There is a frequent area of selling vegetables by bid system.\n\n==Transportation==\n\nSubhash Chander Bhatheja is a very famous    ( 40 years old ) Bus Transporter At Sri Karanpur .His Firm's name Is Subhash Motors . Mr.Subhash G Is A Down To Earth Personality With The Knowledge Of Entire Indian Roads ( Villages ,Tehsils ,Districts ,States )  . He Has more  Knowledge Than Google Regarding Transports .You Can Call To Him At Their Personal Phone Numbers for Advices and  Buses Bookings ,Trucks Etc  = 9413934447 , 7504371313 ...  \n\n\nBy Train - there is direct train from [[Delhi Sarai Rohilla railway station]] [DEE] to Sri Karanpur. Train no 12455/56 [[Delhi Sarai rohila]]  to [[Bikaner]] superfast express and from Sri Ganganagar few passenger trains to Suratgarh goes via Sri Karanpur. The train come from [[Hanumangarh jn.]] to here\n\nTrain no.17623/24 [[Srigangangar]] to [[Hajur Sahib Nanded]] weekliy superfast via [[Suratgarh]] [[Bikaner]]  [[Ahmedabad]] [[Vadodara]] \n\nTrain no. 54761 [[hanumangarh]] to [[Suratgarh]] via [[Sri Ganganagar]]\n \ntrain no. 16311/12 [[Sri Ganganagar]] to [[kochuwali (kerla)]] weekliy superfast train\n\nBy Bus - There is single direct bus to Hisar from Karanpur at morning 6. and a kind of frequent buses throughout the day for Sri Ganganagar.\nDirect bus from Sri Karanpur to [[Hanumangarh]], [[Padampur, Rajasthan|Padampur]], [[Gajsinghpur]], [[RaisinghNagar]], [[Samja Kothi]], [[Rawla]], [[Darshana]], [[Khajuwala]], [[Bikaner]], [[Kesrisinghpur]], etc.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Sri Ganganagar district}}\n\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Sri Ganganagar district]]\n\n\n{{Rajasthan-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{About|the city|the tehsil|Karanpur tehsil}}\n{{Cleanup|date=April 2011}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2018}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=May 2018}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name                    = Karanpur\n| native_name             = Sri Karanpur \n| artist_from_karanpur    = Onenesslover \n| settlement_type         = city\n| image_skyline           = \n| image_alt               = \n| image_caption           = \n| pushpin_map             = India Rajasthan#India\n| pushpin_label_position  = right\n| pushpin_map_alt         = \n| pushpin_map_caption     = Location in Rajasthan, India\n| coordinates             = {{coord|29.8414|N|73.4547|E|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type        = Country\n| subdivision_name        = {{flag|India}}\n| subdivision_type1       = [[States and territories of India|State]]\n| subdivision_name1       = [[Rajasthan]]\n| subdivision_type2       = [[List of districts of India|District]]\n| subdivision_name2       = [[Ganganagar district|Ganganagar]]\n| established_title       = <!-- Established -->\n| established_date        = \n| founder                 = \n| named_for               = \n| government_type         = \n| governing_body          = \n| unit_pref               = Metric\n| area_footnotes          = \n| area_rank               = \n| area_total_km2          = \n| elevation_footnotes     = \n| elevation_m             = 185\n| population_total        = 20694\n| population_as_of        = 2001\n| population_rank         = \n| population_density_km2  = auto\n| population_demonym      = \n| population_footnotes    = \n| demographics_type1      = Languages\n| demographics1_title1    = Official\n| demographics1_info1     = [[Hindi language|Hindi]]\n| timezone1               =