{"title_page": "Yoshiko Honda-Mikami", "text_new": "{{short description|Japanese biathlete}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name        = Yoshiko Honda-Mikami\n| full_name   = \n| image       = \n| caption     = \n| nationality = Japanese\n| sport       = [[Biathlon]]\n| event       = \n| club        = \n| collegeteam =\n| birth_date  = {{birth date and age|1966|5|23|df=yes}}\n| birth_place = \n| death_date  = \n| death_place = \n| height      =\n| weight      =\n}}\n\n'''Yoshiko Honda-Mikami''' (born 23 May 1966) is a Japanese [[Biathlon|biathlete]]. She competed at the [[1992 Winter Olympics]] and the [[1994 Winter Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ho/yoshiko-honda-mikami-1.html |title=Yoshiko Honda-Mikami Olympic Results |accessdate=20 November 2017}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Honda-Mikami, Yoshiko}}\n[[Category:1966 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Biathletes at the 1992 Winter Olympics]]\n[[Category:Biathletes at the 1994 Winter Olympics]]\n[[Category:Japanese female biathletes]]\n[[Category:Olympic biathletes of Japan]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing (living people)]]\n[[Category:Asian Games medalists in cross-country skiing]]\n[[Category:Cross-country skiers at the 1990 Asian Winter Games]]\n[[Category:Asian Games gold medalists for Japan]]\n[[Category:Asian Games silver medalists for Japan]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 1990 Asian Winter Games]]\n{{Japan-biathlon-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Japanese biathlete}}\n{{use dmy dates|date=November 2017}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name        = Yoshiko Honda-Mikami\n| full_name   = \n| image       = \n| caption     = \n| nationality = Japanese\n| sport       = [[Biathlon]]\n| event       = \n| club        = \n| collegeteam =\n| birth_date  = {{birth date and age|1966|5|23|df=yes}}\n| birth_place = \n| death_date 